{{Unreferenced|date = August 2009}}
The '''Jenin Sport Club ''' is a [[Association football|football]] club from the city of [[Jenin]] [[West Bank]], founded in 1945. It is the oldest club in the West Bank.{{Citation needed|date=August 2009}} The team plays in the [[West Bank Premier League]]. The team's ground is the Abu Ammar Stadium in the city of [[Jenin]] .

