*'''[[Tanzanian Premier League]] : 1'''
:: 1984.

*'''[[Zanzibar Premier League]] : 4'''
:: 1984, 1986, 2004, 2013.

*'''[[Nyerere Cup]] : 3'''
:: 1977, 1982, 1983.

*'''[[Mapinduzi Cup]] : 1'''
:: 2002.

