{{Unreferenced|date=November 2006}}
'''Stade Huye''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Butare]], [[Rwanda]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Mukura Victory Sports FC]] and INTARE FC.  The stadium holds 20 000 people.

